thread.title: Woman wounds three at YouTube, then kills herself

title: Woman wounds three at YouTube, then kills herself
text:
Woman wounds three at YouTube, then kills herself Tuesday, April 03, 2018 - 01:20 
A woman opened fire at YouTube's headquarters near San Francisco on Tuesday, wounding three people before taking her own life as employees of the Silicon Valley technology company fled into the surrounding streets, authorities said.
